%vec2norm       Compute the 1-norm of the column vectors in a md-array.
%
%   arr2norm = vec2norm(array)
%
%   arr2norm    The 1-norm of each column vector in array. 
%
%   array       The multi-dimensional array to be measured.
%
%
%   vec2norm computes the 1-norm of each column vector in a multi-dimensional
%   array.
%
%   Calls: none.
%
%   Bugs: none known.

